<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/30380948">有哪些可以满足中二情结的日常用品？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="4334702" data-action="/question/detail">


<textarea class="content hidden">&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;1136&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; src=&quot;//pic2.zhimg.com/3de93086a2fbaeca27d88ffcd66bd369_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;//pic2.zhimg.com/3de93086a2fbaeca27d88ffcd66bd369_r.jpg&quot;&gt;配图为“星球大战睡袍”&lt;br&gt;还有什么日用品这么中二.最好是在室内用的，室外还是低调点好。&lt;br&gt;p.s. cosplay之类的就算了，不实用。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;实用又低调的中二方法&lt;br&gt;&lt;img data-rawheight=&quot;1136&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; src=&quot;//pic3.zhimg.com/65822f2b0646ad74c31a39ad4f2dfbaa_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;//pic3.zhimg.com/65822f2b0646ad74c31a39ad4f2dfbaa_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;别在书包带上，背起书包的那一刻就觉得自己真的是King's hand&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;---------------------------中二的东西和值得推荐的东西并不一样---------------------</textarea>
