</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="4334702" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">1.【精灵球】挂件<br><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/e0e3c820bd767022341cb33f49898606_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="310" data-rawheight="310" class="content_image" width="310">就决定是你了！去吧！中二病！<br><br><br>2.【EVA】冰箱贴<br><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/c57376605205cf4ca3c22eb6bec29526_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="292" data-rawheight="373" class="content_image" width="292">食物紧缺！立即准备！<br><br><br>3.【七龙珠】宝宝围嘴<img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/e209992df693f7c68605436539e856e6_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="310" data-rawheight="310" class="content_image" width="310">你看什么？没对象还想有孩子？<br><br><br>4.【美少女战士】化妆镜<img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/f91cd36521cc5956ceda1a86dfb8ecd3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="423" data-rawheight="600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="423" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/f91cd36521cc5956ceda1a86dfb8ecd3_r.jpg">然而，照了也没有成为美少女。<br><br><br>5.【坂田银时】短裤<img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/38c80e8540814e0f83adbe96d0a047e3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="310" data-rawheight="310" class="content_image" width="310"><br>答应我，请务必穿着出去。<br><br><br>6.【夜光】雨衣<img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/90474f5ea1df3b9d0c3c341627a5396d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/90474f5ea1df3b9d0c3c341627a5396d_r.jpg">就算穿雨衣出门，里面也一定要穿上衣服呢。<br><br><br>7.【RPG游戏】像素地毯<br><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/3ab1720260dbb6443f4d28f36e448f4b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/3ab1720260dbb6443f4d28f36e448f4b_r.jpg">使用Z键调查，发现隐藏任务。<br><br><br>8.【lol】龙龟帽子<img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/5dcb70fcc55e68a8ba24601c8f582a17_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="410" data-rawheight="410" class="content_image" width="410">脑补戴着大喊：TSM！TSM！TSM！<br><br><br>9.【神探夏洛克】221B手机壳<img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/79bc840af0ba0657dbd8bf69fbc9fc4f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="500" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/79bc840af0ba0657dbd8bf69fbc9fc4f_r.jpg">啧啧，整条街的智商都被我带起来了。<br><br><br>10.二次元【漫画】效果包<br><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/bbcd6639e8f02af59fe622dd94c07d3b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="310" data-rawheight="370" class="content_image" width="310">质量差价参差不齐，购买要筛选。<br><br><br>11.【狮虎兽】鬃毛<br><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/350d4c245cbb8de2ab4a628bb01d090f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="365" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/350d4c245cbb8de2ab4a628bb01d090f_r.jpg">呵呵，人仗狗势的时刻来了！<br><br><br>12.【封印】胶带<br><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/fdc4875e26e2549436d9887d96160058_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/fdc4875e26e2549436d9887d96160058_r.jpg">恶灵退散，ICBM！<br><br><br>13.【魔法少女樱】手杖圆珠笔<br><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/28367c5c1aff79a518c8482524941f3a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="589" data-rawheight="591" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="589" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/28367c5c1aff79a518c8482524941f3a_r.jpg">并没有什么用，该写的字一个都不能少。<br><br><br>14.【宫崎骏】伞<br><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/7c4301b762fae872509380280e26c5b5_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="310" data-rawheight="310" class="content_image" width="310"><br>外面黑色里面彩色太赞，有种从现实进入童话的感觉。<br><br><br>15.【神盾局特工】证件夹<img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/8cc54b360654473343763406c8d0a1f2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/8cc54b360654473343763406c8d0a1f2_r.jpg">打开的时候动作大一点，一定要让旁边的人看到。<br><br><br>16.和风【狐狸】面具<br><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/2d177ae7309f5591bd93709fd6dfcf49_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="430" data-rawheight="395" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="430" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/2d177ae7309f5591bd93709fd6dfcf49_r.jpg">正确姿势为斜着遮住2/3的脸，前提是英俊的话。<br><br><br>17.【忍者飞镖】冰箱贴<img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/cc4893b22d5158321a86d640c6d926a6_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="358" data-rawheight="358" class="content_image" width="358">再来找吃的，明年的今天就是你的祭日！<br><br><br>18.【龙猫】围裙<br><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/0622bb5ebd92901f792457b39342afa0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/0622bb5ebd92901f792457b39342afa0_r.jpg">可能穿着就会爱上做饭哦，所以我不会买的。<br><br><br>19.【中二语录】文字T恤<br><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/d0dbd7225781e3aee2541cff3682efe0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="543" data-rawheight="600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="543" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/d0dbd7225781e3aee2541cff3682efe0_r.jpg">关键词一定要是：自由、作战等，最好是毛笔字。<br><br><br>20.【胸部/臀部】鼠标垫<br><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/421a4825a0e76a7122583abab4ae58a8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="400" class="content_image" width="400">没有这个还敢自称宅男？我一个女的都有好几个！<br>我不是说那什么有好几个！你们！！上图上图！！！<br><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/6c278a60aeda60647675c1d701293df5_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="716" data-rawheight="708" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="716" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/6c278a60aeda60647675c1d701293df5_r.jpg"><br><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/8af010cd850e8ec958ddc83ce38c540a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="720" data-rawheight="713" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="720" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/8af010cd850e8ec958ddc83ce38c540a_r.jpg"><br><br>其他答案我看的不太仔细，如果有重复的那就不好意思了。<br>黑暗势力已经开始行动，我必须去战斗！！<br>不用管我！你们的明天，由我来守护！
